          }
        },
        "text_K4frme": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Your feet are 3-dimensional, and so are your shoes. So, there’s a lot more to getting the right fit than just length and width. For an optimal fit, all aspects of the foot need to be considered including: dorsal, plantar, anterior, posterior, medial and lateral.</p>",
            "text_font": "body",
            "text_size": "subtext-md",
