        },
        "text_cq7E3b": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>An optimal fit reduces over-pronation and helps provide proper body alignment. Helping the foot stay close to the neutral position of the subtalar joint will also prevent excessive stretching of the plantar fascia and reduce stress to the knees, hips and back.</p>",
            "text_font": "body",
            "text_size": "subtext-md",
            "text_max_size": 32,
